{"tid":2352670,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[博屌]真心覺得姜濤啲歌好聽過林家謙","createTime":"2021-01-04T07:33:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T09:13:51.000Z","uid":197333,"like":13,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eec034016407a17e60b893c283cff59be3439552","tid":2352670,"uid":197333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:33:17.000Z","msg":"我知道呢個topic同博屌冇分叫,希望各位屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說因為前幾日叱咤同連登討論嘅關係,所以都想聽下林家謙嘅歌(我playlist入面嘅廣東歌仲係停留喺張國榮同eason嘅年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n咁我就喺youtube music搵咗幾首應該係最hit嗰幾首,分別係拼命無恙,一人之境同下一位前度<br />\n<br />\n頭兩首都覺得都還可以,雖然唔會中意聽但都唔覺得難聽,但下一位前度真係搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我原意係想搵啲新嘅廣東歌聽下,叫做支持下香港本地音樂,所以都順手搵埋姜濤啲歌聽,話曬都拎咗最喜愛的男歌手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一聽之下雖然都唔係話好好聽(我聽咗蒙著嘴同亞特蘭提斯),但覺得點都係易入口過林家謙,於是上連登search下,就發現自己好似去咗平行時空咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以出個po問下到底係林家謙有啲好歌我未聽過定還是係其實有巴打都同我有類似嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家屌細力啲,以上係個人感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />細佬係虛心求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5ac2793b1425fa0f0b9687204d1bd94a0549ce","tid":2352670,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:34:41.000Z","msg":"潛水"},{"pid":"a4af0642dcdea24ff035fabe9b7553d12247219b","tid":2352670,"uid":87155,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T07:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gi